Source: aardmail
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Bernd Wachter <bwachter-pkg@lart.info>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), libssl-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.3

Package: aardmail
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Mail related tools like a pop3-client to retrieve mails
 aardmail is a package with useful tools for different kinds of mailhandling. 
 Currently included are pop3c, a client to retrieve mails from a pop3 server, 
 and miniclient for testing connectiens. All programs are SSL-enabled.

Package: aardmail-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: aardmail (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Debug symbols for aardmail

